      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments performed with blood analogue fluid at physiological hematocrit and shear history representative of VAD operation.",
      "rationale": "Validation used glycerol-water analogue; hematocrit effects and red blood cell deformability not represented, reducing relevance."
