      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence residuals below 1e-6 for all transport equations; floating-point sensitivity analysis documented.",
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence not systematically documented for hemolysis scalar; floating-point sensitivity analysis not performed. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
