      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mechanistic justification for power-law hemolysis model selection with sensitivity to model-form alternatives documented.",
      "rationale": "Power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger model selected without documented comparison to alternative mechanistic models; model-form uncertainty unquantified."
