      "acceptanceCriteria": "Probability distributions assigned to all uncertain input parameters; global sensitivity analysis completed.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo sweep performed on rotational speed only; blood viscosity, hematocrit, and power-law exponents treated as fixed. Global sensitivity not completed."
